history.content:
Options only works if there is a seat available. If you were to change it a waitlisted section it would drop you out again and waitlist you for both the lab and the lecture. 

On a side note, I am not sure about CS 10 but most classes allow you to attend any lab or section with priority being given to students enrolled in that section if the room overflows.

I am currently enrolled in CS10, but I want to switch my Discussion & Lab sessions to one that has a waitlist (because my current ones have a timing conflict). If I switch it under options on calcentral, will I be dropped out of CS10 and on the waitlist again, or will I still be enrolled in CS10 and only switch over when there is a free position?
history.subject: CS10: Swapping Discussion/Lab
